                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, N</hi> 76). I produce a certificate of the prisoner's conviction—(<hi rend="italic">Read—Convicted June</hi>, 1846, <hi rend="italic">and confined six months</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
